- title "Clients"

%p.tile
  Whether it was graphics or a full production, we have done work for these people on some capacity over the last few years.
  %span.hide-mobile Click below for some testimonials.

.clients

  - @clients.each_with_index do |client, index|

    .client.tile{ class: ("has-description" if client.description.present?) }
      .overlay
      = image_tag client.logo_url
    .client-description
      %h3.client-name= client.name
      - if client.description.present?
        %p.client-description= client.description
        .hide-mobile
          .client-author
            %h3.client-name
              = client.person
              - if client.website.present?
                %br/
                = link_to client.website, client.website

          - if client.video.present?
            .play-film
              %h3.client-name= link_to "play film", client.video

.client-info.description
